We are Excellence-oriented Canadian nationwide bathtub refinishing company and proud Montrealers. The home of the ECO-CASTING ; A permanent synthetic porcelain resurfacing system. Our innovative bathtub refinishing process is Odorless, non-toxic and safe. Our refinished bathtubs are as beautiful and durable as new and will last you for a lifetime with no peeling concern.

Join hundreds of existing satisfied customers and send us your bathtub/sink picture for a free online estimate.

We are proud to also render professional surface spot repair for Acrylic surfaces. We resolve cracks,dents, chips, burns, stains and more.
All our work is guaranteed and certified by the major acrylic bath brands.
